result.name: 1990-1990-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-bristol-channel-we-08-1990
result.notes:
Analysis of plankton samples collected on one in a series of surveys in 1990 
to determine the extent and timing of sole (Solea solea) spawning. Numbers of 
ichthyoplankton, Nephrops larvae and edible crab (Cancer pagurus), along with 
associated positional and environmental data (temperature and salinity).
